description:
Enhance test coverage for short hash resolution with property-based testing using proptest.

Current: 14 unit tests provide good coverage with specific test cases.

Enhancement: Add property-based tests for additional confidence:
- Random UUID generation with varying prefix lengths (4-16 chars)
- Automatic edge case discovery
- Verify resolution correctness across large input space
- Test ambiguity detection with random collision scenarios

Example test:
```rust
proptest! {
    #[test]
    fn test_resolve_random_prefixes(prefix_len in 4usize..16) {
        // Generate random UUIDs, test various prefix lengths
        // Verify unique prefixes resolve correctly
        // Verify ambiguous prefixes fail appropriately
    }
}
```

Priority: Low - current unit tests are thorough and comprehensive.

References: docs/session-2025-12-21-short-hash-progress.md (Issue #2)
